snippet.title: Fear The Night [PC] Debut Trailer
snippet.description:
Fear the Night is a free-to-play open world survival game filled with blood-thirsty zombies, deadly rogue robots, and uncharted, precious environments necessary for survival.

Fear the Night is available now on Steam Early Access ( https://store.steampowered.com/app/764920/Fear_the_Night/ ) for $11.24.
